7
00:01:25,120 --> 00:01:25,480
Speak!

8
00:01:28,520 --> 00:01:29,160
Yes.

9
00:01:30,440 --> 00:01:31,680
I was the one who killed her.

10
00:01:32,160 --> 00:01:33,760
