11
00:01:34,360 --> 00:01:35,960
Because she killed my son.

12
00:01:38,640 --> 00:01:40,560
Xiao Yuejiao and my son, Wang Wei,

13
00:01:42,680 --> 00:01:45,360
were fellow apprentices learning opera together since childhood.

14
00:01:46,080 --> 00:01:47,320
They were childhood sweethearts,

15
00:01:48,400 --> 00:01:49,440
and had feelings for each other.

16
00:01:50,720 --> 00:01:51,960
But Xiao Yuejiao,

17
00:01:52,760 --> 00:01:54,440
after meeting many wealthy bosses,

18
00:01:55,080 --> 00:01:56,240
began to treat my son

19
00:01:56,600 --> 00:01:58,000
