20
00:01:58,640 --> 00:02:01,040
My son couldn't accept it.

21
00:02:01,280 --> 00:02:02,920
So he went to her for an explanation.

22
00:02:03,680 --> 00:02:04,480
Very nice.

23
00:02:05,200 --> 00:02:05,680
Yuejiao!

24
00:02:05,920 --> 00:02:06,960
You can't go with him!

25
00:02:10,160 --> 00:02:11,000
Is this pretty boy

26
00:02:11,200 --> 00:02:12,160
