27
00:02:13,200 --> 00:02:14,480
What paramour?

28
00:02:14,720 --> 00:02:15,800
I don't even know him.

29
00:02:17,240 --> 00:02:18,760
From beginning to end,

30
00:02:19,080 --> 00:02:21,320
