31
00:02:22,360 --> 00:02:23,280
You little vixen.

32
00:02:23,800 --> 00:02:25,280
You adulterers!

33
00:02:25,480 --> 00:02:25,880
You...

34
00:02:26,000 --> 00:02:26,400
You...

35
00:02:34,240 --> 00:02:35,600
They beat my son until he was

36
00:02:35,600 --> 00:02:36,800
