37
00:02:40,920 --> 00:02:41,400
Mom...

38
00:02:41,880 --> 00:02:42,360
Yes...

39
00:02:47,720 --> 00:02:48,640
I'm sorry.

40
00:02:50,800 --> 00:02:51,520
I can't provide for you

41
00:02:53,280 --> 00:02:53,880
in your old age,

42
00:02:56,640 --> 00:02:57,480
or bury you.

43
00:03:11,400 --> 00:03:12,960
I went to her to demand an explanation.

44
00:03:16,280 --> 00:03:17,400
But they

45
00:03:18,280 --> 00:03:20,400
had already taken Xiao Yuejiao

46
00:03:20,520 --> 00:03:22,160
and left.

47
00:03:29,040 --> 00:03:30,760
So later, when Uncle Qin told me

48
00:03:32,440 --> 00:03:33,680
that Xiao Yuejiao had returned,

49
00:03:35,480 --> 00:03:36,480
I went to the theater.

50
00:03:38,160 --> 00:03:39,200
I waited until night,

51
00:03:39,600 --> 00:03:41,640
grabbed a cleaver from the kitchen,

52
00:03:42,520 --> 00:03:43,840
rushed into her room,

53
00:03:44,600 --> 00:03:45,960
and killed her.

54
00:03:47,480 --> 00:03:48,480
Did you use this knife

55
00:03:48,480 --> 00:03:49,680
to kill Xiao Yuejiao?

56
00:03:50,600 --> 00:03:51,200
Yes.

57
00:03:52,000 --> 00:03:53,040
It was this cleaver.

58
00:03:53,560 --> 00:03:55,200
But the fatal wound on her neck

59
00:03:55,520 --> 00:03:56,760
was caused by a Guan blade.

60
00:03:57,200 --> 00:03:58,080
So who slashed her with that?

61
00:03:58,520 --> 00:03:59,240
It was me.

62
00:04:00,880 --> 00:04:02,800
I avenged my son.

63
00:04:04,000 --> 00:04:05,000
With this cleaver,

64
00:04:05,800 --> 00:04:06,840
