66
00:04:09,000 --> 00:04:10,040
I borrowed Lord Guan's broadsword.

67
00:04:11,400 --> 00:04:12,880
I hacked and hacked!

68
00:04:14,320 --> 00:04:15,120
Then where did you get

69
00:04:15,120 --> 00:04:16,120
this Guan blade from?

70
00:04:16,760 --> 00:04:17,160
Furthermore,

71
00:04:17,560 --> 00:04:19,160
why would you carry two

72
00:04:19,160 --> 00:04:20,160
