73
00:04:20,440 --> 00:04:20,960
Could it be

74
00:04:21,760 --> 00:04:22,960
you knew from the start

75
00:04:23,760 --> 00:04:25,040
that a cleaver couldn't kill Xiao Yuejiao?

76
00:04:27,880 --> 00:04:29,000
I killed her!

77
00:04:29,400 --> 00:04:30,320
It was me!

78
00:04:30,640 --> 00:04:32,200
I killed her!

79
00:04:32,280 --> 00:04:33,440
Arrest me!

80
00:04:33,600 --> 00:04:35,600
I avenged my son!

81
00:04:35,600 --> 00:04:38,280
I killed Xiao Yuejiao!

82
00:04:38,880 --> 00:04:39,480
I killed her!

83
00:04:39,720 --> 00:04:40,760
I took Lord Guan's broadsword!

84
00:04:40,760 --> 00:04:41,080
I hacked!

85
00:04:41,080 --> 00:04:41,480
Chuncheng,

86
00:04:41,800 --> 00:04:42,640
- I hacked! - Take her into custody first.

87
00:04:44,640 --> 00:04:46,400
Mom avenged you, son!

88
00:04:54,600 --> 00:04:55,200
Inspector Huang.

89
00:04:58,920 --> 00:04:59,400
Inspector.

90
00:04:59,880 --> 00:05:01,000
Why did we only take Auntie Wang

91
00:05:01,000 --> 00:05:01,600
into custody,

92
00:05:01,800 --> 00:05:02,440
instead of

93
00:05:02,720 --> 00:05:03,520
officially charging her?

94
00:05:04,200 --> 00:05:05,560
Because she only injured Xiao Yuejiao,

95
00:05:06,040 --> 00:05:07,040
and is not her

96
00:05:07,040 --> 00:05:07,760
true killer.

97
00:05:11,400 --> 00:05:12,040
Moreover,

98
00:05:12,800 --> 00:05:13,520
