99
00:05:13,520 --> 00:05:14,680
who the real killer is.

100
00:05:15,680 --> 00:05:16,800
But because she's eager to die,

101
00:05:17,320 --> 00:05:18,760
she took all the blame

102
00:05:19,320 --> 00:05:20,640
upon herself.

103
00:05:31,560 --> 00:05:32,400
Please bless me.

104
00:05:36,000 --> 00:05:36,600
Boss Mei.

105
00:05:40,960 --> 00:05:41,640
Brother Bao.

106
00:05:42,040 --> 00:05:43,120
Why are you out of the hospital?

107
00:05:45,240 --> 00:05:45,520
Your...

108
00:05:46,280 --> 00:05:47,680
