132
00:06:39,640 --> 00:06:40,160
Not enough.

133
00:06:41,000 --> 00:06:42,360
Of course it's not enough.

134
00:06:46,960 --> 00:06:48,240
But what I can give you

135
00:06:49,200 --> 00:06:50,280
