147
00:07:16,920 --> 00:07:17,800
I will definitely treat you well.

148
00:07:18,000 --> 00:07:18,440
Okay?

149
00:07:19,640 --> 00:07:20,360
Let go of me!

150
00:07:20,720 --> 00:07:21,840
Let go of me!

151
00:07:28,680 --> 00:07:29,360
Let go of me!

152
00:07:38,960 --> 00:07:40,440
If you dare to take one more step,

153
00:07:41,000 --> 00:07:42,120
