168
00:08:32,600 --> 00:08:33,080
Who's there?

169
00:08:34,120 --> 00:08:34,880
Stop right there!

170
00:08:43,560 --> 00:08:44,120
Who is it?

171
00:08:44,880 --> 00:08:46,160
