172
00:09:02,080 --> 00:09:03,040
Murder!

173
00:09:03,520 --> 00:09:04,520
Murder!

174
00:09:06,200 --> 00:09:07,600
The fatal wound on his body

175
00:09:07,720 --> 00:09:09,200
