176
00:09:09,680 --> 00:09:10,240
However,

177
00:09:10,240 --> 00:09:11,480
judging from the depth of the wound,

178
00:09:11,720 --> 00:09:13,200
the killer had immense strength,

179
00:09:13,760 --> 00:09:14,400
and towards Brother Bao,

180
00:09:14,720 --> 00:09:15,680
