187
00:09:33,560 --> 00:09:34,640
Has he offended anyone?

188
00:09:36,440 --> 00:09:36,800
This...

189
00:09:36,880 --> 00:09:37,240
I...

190
00:09:37,280 --> 00:09:38,200
