193
00:09:42,240 --> 00:09:44,160
Plus, with his temper,

194
00:09:46,240 --> 00:09:46,840
maybe...

195
00:09:53,480 --> 00:09:54,080
Boss Mei,

196
00:09:56,160 --> 00:09:57,240
